def δ (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  if h : x ≠ 0 then
    Nat.find_greatest (fun d => odd d ∧ d ∣ x) x
  else
    1

def δ (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  if h : x > 0 then
    Nat.find (Exists.intro ((∃ d : ℕ, d ∣ x ∧ d % 2 = 1) → True) (by
      cases Nat.exists_odd_factor x h with
      | intro d hd => exact ⟨d, hd.left, hd.right⟩))
  else 0

def δ (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  if h : x > 0 then
    Finset.max' (Finset.filter (λ d, d ∣ x ∧ d % 2 = 1) (Finset.range (x + 1))) (by simp [h])
  else
    0

def δ (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  if h : x ≠ 0 then
    Finset.max' (Finset.filter (λ d, d % 2 = 1) (Finset.divisors x)) (by
      obtain ⟨d, hd⟩ := Nat.exists_odd_factor x h
      exact Finset.mem_filter.mpr ⟨Finset.mem_divisors.mpr ⟨hd, Nat.pos_of_ne_zero h⟩, Nat.odd_iff.mp hd⟩)
  else 1

def δ (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  if h : x = 0 then 0 else
  let divisors := (Finset.filter (λ d, d ∣ x ∧ d % 2 = 1) (Finset.range (x + 1))) in
  Finset.max' divisors (Finset.nonempty_of_mem (Finset.mem_filter.2 ⟨Nat.dvd_refl x, Nat.odd_one⟩))

def δ (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  if h : x > 0 then
    Nat.find_greatest (fun d => d ∣ x ∧ d % 2 = 1) x
  else
    0
